{"article_id":"xh6BqnjGwzcgoCXq","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Retired Lt. Gen Michael Flynn has promised \" full cooperation \" in the special counsel ' s Russia investigation","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"and ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"according to a confidant ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"is prepared to testify","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"that Donald Trump directed him to make contact with the Russians , initially as a way","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"to work together","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"to fight ISIS in Syria .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Interested in Russia Investigation ?","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Add Russia Investigation as an interest","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest Russia Investigation news , video , and analysis from .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Add Interest","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"The stunning turn comes","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"as Flynn pleaded guilty to one count of lying to the FBI about his back-channel negotiations with the Russian ambassador","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"- talks","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"that occurred","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"before Trump took office .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"The special counsel made the plea agreement public Friday morning .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The confidant provided with new details on Friday about Trump ' s instructions to Flynn .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"During the campaign , Trump asked Flynn to be one of a small group of close advisors","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"charged with improving relations in Russia and other hot spots .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"The source said","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Trump phoned Flynn shortly after the election","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"to explicitly ask him to \" serve as point person on Russia , \"","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"and to reach out personally to Russian officials","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"to develop strategies","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"to jointly combat ISIS .","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"The confidant told","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that Flynn felt abandoned by Trump in recent weeks ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"and told friends about the decision","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"to make the plea deal within the last 24 hours","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"as he grew increasingly concerned about crippling legal costs","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"he would face","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"if he continued to contest the charges .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"\" Flynn is very angry , \"","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"the confidant told Friday .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"\" He will cooperate truthfully on any question","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"they ask him . \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"In a prepared statement , Flynn expressed regret ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"but also stood defiant against the more scurrilous allegations","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that circulated about his work with Russia .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"\" It has been extraordinarily painful to endure these many months of false accusations of ' treason ' and other outrageous acts , \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Flynn said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"\" Such false accusations are contrary to everything","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"I have ever done","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"and stood for .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"But I recognize","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that the actions","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"I acknowledged in court today","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"were wrong ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"and , through my faith in God , I am working to set things right . \"","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Richard Frankel , a former senior aide to Flynn and an contributor , said","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Flynn made his decision to cooperate under immense pressure ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"but he believes","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"it is the right move for the country .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"\" I do n't know","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"how much General Flynn knows about any criminal activity","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"that took place during the campaign or in the White House , \"","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"said Frankel ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"who also served in a senior role at the FBI .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"\" However , General Flynn was a top adviser to President Trump in the campaign and a top adviser to him","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"when he entered into the WH","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"so","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"if there are bodies buried","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"so to speak ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"General Flynn would know about them in my opinion . \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Flynn was charged with lying to the FBI about the nature of his conversations with then-Russian ambassador to the United States Sergey Kislyak during the presidential transition .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Those conversations led Russian officials to temper their response to increased U.S. sanctions ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"according to the charging documents .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The charge carries a penalty of up to five years in prison ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"but according to court documents ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Flynn likely faces a sentence of zero to six months .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"The White House had claimed","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"it was unaware of the substance of those conversations ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"but today ' s court documents show","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Flynn was acting specifically at the direction of senior transition team officials .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"On the same day","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"President Obama imposed tough sanctions on Russian facilities in the U.S.","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"for meddling in the election ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"the Russian ambassador called Flynn","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"to talk about them .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"After that conversation , Flynn consulted with a senior transition team official","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"who said","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"the Trump \" did not want Russia to escalate the situation , \"","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"so Flynn relayed the request directly to Kislyak .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Russian officials tempered their response to increased U.S. sanctions ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"and President-elect Trump then tweeted :","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"\" Great move on delay","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"( by V.Putin ) -","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"I always knew","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"he was very smart ! \"","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"The documents also show","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"that \" a very senior member \" of the transition team ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"which has learned","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"was Trump ' s son-in-law Jared Kushner ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"told Flynn to contact Russia about a United Nations resolution","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"involving Israel .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"The President has denied directing Flynn to make the contacts .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"\" No , I didn ' t direct him , \"","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Trump said in February ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"\" but I would have directed him","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"if he didn ' t do it , okay ? \"","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Flynn became the latest and most-senior Trump associate","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"to face charges in Mueller 's probe","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"and arrived at the U.S. District courthouse","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"accompanied by his wife and attorney Robert Kelner","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"after having been processed at the FBI Washington Field Office ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"where he was fingerprinted and photographed ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"according to FBI officials .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"In court , the retired lieutenant general was asked by Federal Judge Rudolph Contreras","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"if he had ever been a part of similar proceedings ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"to which Flynn replied","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"that he had not .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Contreras then asked Kelner","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"whether he was correct","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"in assuming","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"that Flynn was pleading guilty .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"After the hearing , Flynn was free to go ,","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"but has to check in with authorities each week .","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"Sentencing has been put off for now","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"- and the judge noted","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"that Flynn is agreeing to cooperate with authorities in other matters .","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"Flynn had initially resisted cooperating with the investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"according to people close to the retired general ,","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"but he has been facing mounting legal debts and plans","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"to sell his house","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"to help defray costs .","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"He only recently learned the full scope of the charges","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"he could potentially face .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"Last week , Trump lawyers received calls from Kelner ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"alerting them","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"that he could no longer participate in information exchanges with other possible Mueller targets , the first public indication","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"that a plea deal was in the works .","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"\" My guilty plea and agreement","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"to cooperate with the Special Counsel 's Office","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"reflect a decision","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"I made in the best interests of my family and of our country , \"","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"Flynn said .","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"\" I accept full responsibility for my actions . \"","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"Trump and his legal team have learned of Flynn 's decision via news reports Friday morning ,","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"according to sources with knowledge of the situation .","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"On Monday , Kelner was spotted exiting a meeting at Mueller ' s offices in Washington ,","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"reported .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"Flynn is a decorated military officer","depth":6},{"id":143,"text":"who once headed the Defense Intelligence Agency","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"and ,","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"after leaving government ,","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"spoke frequently at Trump campaign rallies .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"He began facing scrutiny","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"after it was learned he took payment","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"to attend a Russian television event ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"at which he appeared seated next to Russian President Vladimir Putin .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"That scrutiny only increased","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"after he took over as Trump ' s national security adviser .","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"He was ultimately forced to resign after just a few weeks on the job","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"after it was revealed that he misled Vice President Mike Pence and other administration officials about his meeting with the Russian ambassador .","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Flynn initially denied","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"that he discussed U.S. sanctions","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"placed on Russia","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"with Kislyak ,","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"but transcripts of Flynn and Kislyak ' s phone calls","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"reviewed by Justice Department lawyers","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"showed otherwise .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"Flynn was paid over $ 500,000 by foreign clients for consulting work and speaking fees","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"- including contracts","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"he allegedly failed to list on applications for security clearances and financial disclosure forms .","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"He also only belatedly disclosed lobbying work","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"his firm engaged in on behalf of the Turkish government .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"Trump reportedly attempted to persuade the FBI to drop its investigation into Flynn ' s conduct .","depth":6},{"id":168,"text":"In a Feb. 14 meeting at the White House , Trump reportedly told then-FBI Director James Comey to \" let this go . \"","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"\" I hope","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"you can see your way clear to letting this go ,","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"to letting Flynn go , \"","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"Trump told Comey ,","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"according to a memo","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"Comey wrote afterwards ,","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"which was later described by the New York Times .","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"\" He is a good guy .","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"I hope","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"you can let this go . \"","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"On Oct. 30 , two members of Trump 's campaign staff , former campaign chair Paul Manafort and his longtime associate Rick Gates , were indicted on 12 counts","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"brought by Mueller 's team","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"related to work","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"done prior to joining the Trump campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"including conspiracy against the U.S. , conspiracy","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"to launder money","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"and serving as an unregistered agent of a foreign principal .","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"That same day , it was also revealed that a third Trump campaign adviser , George Papadopoulos , pleaded guilty earlier in the month","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"to making false statements to FBI agents","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"probing his attempts","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"to arrange a meeting between Russian officials and the campaign .","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"Correction :","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"During a live Special Report , reported","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"that a confidant of Lt. Gen. Michael Flynn said","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"Flynn was prepared to testify","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"that then-candidate Donald Trump instructed him to contact Russian officials during the campaign .","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"That source later clarified","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"that during the campaign , Trump assigned Flynn and a small circle of other senior advisers","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"to find ways","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"to repair relations with Russia and other hot spots .","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"It was shortly after the election , that President-elect Trump directed Flynn to contact Russian officials on topics","depth":9},{"id":200,"text":"that included working jointly against ISIS .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":401,"left":207,"right":400,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":0,"right":206,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":206,"left":203,"right":205,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":203,"left":202,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":202,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":4,"right":204,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":400,"left":300,"right":399,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":210,"right":299,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":209,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":7,"right":208,"relation":"condition","